#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:919
msgid ""
"Distance between alignment points in pixels, decoupled from the correlation "
"box (which keeps its full size). 0 = automatic: 2.25 × the correlation box "
"half-width, i.e. 54 px at the default 24. To sample the seeing distortion "
"finer, keep the correlation box at its default size and reduce the pitch — "
